<div class="title">Sleep Aid Comparisons</div>
<div class="substance">Benzodiazepines & Various</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Theodore&Exact=1">Theodore</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Theodore. "Sleep Aid Comparisons: An Experience with Benzodiazepines & Various (exp53482)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 21, 2008. erowid.org/exp/53482</div>

<br/>



